trends: There has been one other sighting in Carteret
There were no other sightings in Carteret on or around July 15th 2001
Summary: Twnty moving lights over Carteret, NJ
divs: Sighting DetailsThe following report was sent to George Filer by Rev Chubenko: I wanted toreport this sighting, since it occurred at approximately 12:45 AM July 15, 2001,over the town of Carteret, New Jersey. I am an Orthodox Ukrainian priest -- andmy son (who is a funeral director was going out on a death call) gets in touchwith me via his cell phone at about 12:40 and tells me I need to get dressedquickly and come outside. He was just getting ready to get on to the New JerseyTurnpike when he saw a huge collection of lights numbering about 30. FatherBelenko went outside and observed numerous lights moving slowly. AT least sixwere dimming and brightening in unison.See complete report in Filers Files 29, 30 31, 32, 33, #34 www.filersfiles.com
